overview: Quick-witted comedy duo, Jess Salomon and Eman El-Husseini, hilariously take-on today’s politics from their perspectives as a Jewish and Palestinian same-sex married couple. From peace in the Middle East, Donald Trump, marriage, and Eman’s reckless driving, this one-hour comedy special from Just For Laughs is sure to leave you in stitches.
title: The El-Salomons: Marriage of Convenience
